snippet.title: 🎵DJ Okawari - Flower Dance | 4hands piano
snippet.description:
Lots of you have been requested this song long time ago, but we put arrangement off due to the difficulties. The original song is for the piano and hard to arrange in 4 hands😭 We hope you have a time to heal with our video☺️

And today, we changed our seat that you asked for😁 It’s like a little gift for whom that couldn’t see our concert💜 
We want to say thank you and sooner or later, a vlog for concert and meeting will be uploaded!
